{"tid":2234784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（選情告急？）川普「美台建交」有可能是更大的10月驚奇","createTime":"2020-10-08T06:50:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T14:49:31.000Z","uid":184679,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cc9b57e139c8605c2da6499ae615ef35e96996da","tid":2234784,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T06:50:00.000Z","msg":"南華早報刊登澳洲格里菲斯大學（Griffith University）國際關係教授Kai He和國際關係高級講師Huiyun Feng投稿，指稱如果美國總統川普的連任希望持續下滑，他有可能走險棋，在外交上承認台灣，真正擔當戰時總統（wartime president）以挽救政治前途。<br />\n<br />\n文中提到美台關係近來升溫：美國8月和9月分別派高階官員出訪台灣；在中國10月1日國慶日的前兩天，美國駐聯合國大使公開支持台灣加入聯合國；另傳川普政府將售台七項武器系統，包括長程飛彈，讓台灣戰機能遠距攻擊中國大陸目標。<br />\n<br />\n川普對台灣的熱情顯然是想刻劃自己「強硬對付中國」的形象。「痛擊中國」能有效幫美國政客集結支持者。川普正全力阻止報稅紀錄公開，但首場辯論表現欠佳，他可能有動機採取較具風險的選項以扭轉情勢，不排除川普可能推動在外交上承認台灣，製造他染疫之外更大的10月驚奇。<br />\n<br />\n台灣獨立會威脅到共產黨統治中國的合法性，習近平別無選擇必須一戰，因台灣問題挑釁激起軍事行動，能讓川普真正取得戰時總統權限，而歷史顯示，在美國，戰時總統較容易贏得連任。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/121687/4919790\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F121687%2F4919790&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5MyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=981a9527\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/121687/4919790</a>"},{"pid":"ec8d8a467645232da2fca95302e2dd29b1365cfd","tid":2234784,"uid":144626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T06:53:25.000Z","msg":"第二加速師 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4258d7d13fb88361f49f43b0b72c845679b1131","tid":2234784,"uid":97979,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T07:34:17.000Z","msg":"其實真係有可能<br />\n尤係係Trump中左武肺之後，俾人Spin咗個話題去抗疫，民望起唔返<br />\n要spin返個話題去外交"},{"pid":"b7f09d6113a8b7a0d7f309ffc5365569a0c1c053","tid":2234784,"uid":85461,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T07:43:32.000Z","msg":"Boris Johnson 中完肺炎就進化<br />\n侵侵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5844c4e39a74ea46cce5ad3d6e5cffa326ca6b5","tid":2234784,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T07:45:21.000Z","msg":"炸佢老母！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f162a07e94bb74eec38b683c5de7eefbc4f0cc99","tid":2234784,"uid":326665,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T07:45:24.000Z","msg":"其實係得返激進一招，咩疫苗，經濟，BLM已經無用"},{"pid":"472e14b33bb23fb1281c61b6d1f899ce08c9c1ea","tid":2234784,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:27:33.000Z","msg":"拜登唔鍾意同台灣建交畫面"},{"pid":"6a451ada32b6b0db882dece2e0dda24905b65cde","tid":2234784,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T14:46:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a141573b1f03f7772ca100a339268479a2f61f16","tid":2234784,"uid":24345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"472e14b33bb23fb1281c61b6d1f899ce08c9c1ea","tid":2234784,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:27:33.000Z","msg":"拜登唔鍾意同台灣建交畫面"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T14:49:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T6jF1SO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT6jF1SO.png&h=71d3d983&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}